00:07:40.100 --> 00:07:41.900
So let's talk about emotions.

00:07:41.900 --> 00:07:43.470
Emotions are a fascinating

00:07:43.470 --> 00:07:45.913
and vital aspect of our life experience.

00:07:45.913 --> 00:07:47.960
It's fair to say that emotions

00:07:47.960 --> 00:07:51.960
make up most of what we think
of as our experience of life,

00:07:51.960 --> 00:07:53.026
even the things we do,

00:07:53.026 --> 00:07:55.077
our behaviors and the places we go,

00:07:55.077 --> 00:07:57.639
and the people we end up
encountering in our life,

00:07:57.639 --> 00:08:02.450
all of that really funnels
into our emotional perception

00:08:02.450 --> 00:08:05.181
of what those things mean,
whether or not they made us happy

00:08:05.181 --> 00:08:10.181
or sad or depressed or
lonely, or were all inspiring.

00:08:10.217 --> 00:08:12.630
Now one thing that is absolutely true

00:08:12.630 --> 00:08:14.820
is that everyone's perception of emotion

00:08:14.820 --> 00:08:16.033
is slightly different.

00:08:16.033 --> 00:08:20.280
Meaning, your idea of happy
is very likely different

00:08:20.280 --> 00:08:23.626
than my idea of what a
state of happiness is.

00:08:23.626 --> 00:08:27.720
And we know this also for
color vision, for instance,

00:08:27.720 --> 00:08:30.098
even though the cells
in your eye and my eye

00:08:30.098 --> 00:08:33.640
that perceive the color red are identical

00:08:33.640 --> 00:08:35.599
right down to the genes that they express,

00:08:35.599 --> 00:08:39.177
we can be certain based
on experimental evidence,

00:08:39.177 --> 00:08:41.186
and what are called
psychophysical studies,

00:08:41.186 --> 00:08:45.540
that your idea of the most intense red

00:08:45.540 --> 00:08:46.570
is going to be very different

00:08:46.570 --> 00:08:48.840
than my idea of the most intense red

00:08:48.840 --> 00:08:51.050
if we were given a selection
of 10 different reds

00:08:51.050 --> 00:08:52.700
and asked which one is most intense,

00:08:52.700 --> 00:08:54.980
which one looks most red,

00:08:54.980 --> 00:08:56.200
and that seems crazy,

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:58.790
you would think that
something as simple as color

00:08:58.790 --> 00:09:00.962
would be universal, and yet it's not.

00:09:00.962 --> 00:09:03.135
And so we need to agree at the outset

00:09:03.135 --> 00:09:07.450
that emotions are complicated
and yet they are tractable.

00:09:07.450 --> 00:09:08.650
They can be understood.

